      "docs": "<b>Allowed roles:</b> FRONTEND (all parties), BACKEND<br/>\nSeries of validations (preflight check) is performed on binder with status IN_PREPARATION.\nResponse clearly indicates if binder is ready to be FINALISED or if some changes are still needed.\n"
    },
    {
