      "docs": "<b>Allowed roles:</b> FRONTEND (OWNER only), BACKEND<br/>\nUpdate input.\n<ul>\n   <li>An input can be updated only when the binder that contains it is in the `IN_PREPARATION` state.</li>\n   <li>Updates comply with RFC-7396</li>\n </ul>\n"
    },
